Home page featuring the Hero section with video background placeholder, Fleet preview, Services grid, Service areas strip, and a Booking preview widget. 

#### [NEW] [fleet.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/fleet.html)
Showcase of the luxury vehicles with specs (passenger/luggage capacity) and booking links.

#### [NEW] [services.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/services.html)
Detailed breakdown of offerings: Airport Transfers, Corporate Travel, Events, Hourly.

#### [NEW] [booking.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/booking.html)
Full interactive booking form with polished inputs for location, dates, times, and vehicle selection.

#### [NEW] [corporate.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/corporate.html)
Information tailored for B2B clients, featuring an inquiry form.

#### [NEW] [about.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/about.html)
Brand story, commitment to luxury, and safety standards.

#### [NEW] [contact.html](file:///c:/Users/ashle/OneDrive/Documents/Antigravity/dap-executive/contact.html)
