## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
Not applicable for a static vanilla HTML/CSS site, though we will validate the HTML for strictness using W3C standards implicitly by writing semantic tags.

### Manual Verification
1. I will use the browser tool to open `index.html` locally and verify the layout, typography, and color palette.
2. I will capture a screenshot of the hero section with the browser tool.
3. Once completed, you can open `c:\Users\ashle\OneDrive\Documents\Antigravity\dap-executive\index.html` in your own browser to review the design and responsiveness.
